<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.7">
<l>nōyelām peytatō rākkaiyai meyyeṉak koṇṭu vāḷā</l>
<l>pēyartām pēcumap pēccainī piḻaiyeṉak karuti ṉāyēl</l>
<l>tīyulām veṅkatirt tiṅkaḷāy maṅkulvā ṉāki niṉṟa</l>
<l>māyaṉār vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you think that those useless words spoken by madmen,</l>
<l>Holding that a body pervaded with every ailment is real, are wrong,</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ,</l>
<l rend="indent">[the city of] the dark one</l>
<l>Who endures as the sun, hot like fire, as the moon, and as the cloudy sky.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
